snippet.title: The Rich Lifestyle of Uma Thurman 2022
snippet.description:
Uma Thurman’s lifestyle in 2022
Uma Thurman is an American actress and model. She has performed in a variety of films, ranging from romantic comedies and dramas to science fiction and action movies. Following her appearances on the covers of British Vogue, she starred in Dangerous Liaisons (1988). Thurman rose to international prominence with her performance in Quentin Tarantino’s Pulp Fiction (1994), for which she was nominated for several prestigious awards.
